  "text": "Physical Therapy In-Person Visit Checklist (By\n Body Part)\nThis document is optimized for RAG search testing. It includes structured, condition-based physical\ntherapy equipment, exercises, and tools categorized by body part for in-person visits.\nGeneral Physical Therapy Essentials\n- Portable therapy mat or foldable exercise mat\n- Resistance bands (light, medium, heavy)\n- Hand sanitizer, PPE, disinfectant wipes\n- Tablet with EMR access and therapy tracking apps\n- Pain scale charts and functional assessment forms\n- Stopwatch or timer for exercise tracking\nKnee Physical Therapy\n- Knee strengthening bands and loops\n- Balance board or wobble cushion\n- Cold therapy packs\n- Patellar tracking braces\n- Step platform for rehab exercises\n- Exercise sheets: quad sets, hamstring curls, lunges\nBack (Spine) Physical Therapy\n- Lumbar rolls and posture supports\n- Foam rollers for spine mobilization\n- Stretching straps\n- Core strengthening tools (medicine ball optional)\n- TENS unit for pain relief\n- Exercise sheets: pelvic tilts, bridges, cat-cow stretches\nShoulder Physical Therapy\n- Shoulder pulley system\n- Light dumbbells (1-5 lbs)\n- Resistance bands for rotator cuff strengthening\n- Hot/cold packs\n- Range of motion sticks\n- Exercise sheets: arm raises, rotations, wall climbs\nNeck (Cervical) Physical Therapy\n- Cervical pillow or support\n- Resistance bands (light)\n\n- Massage tools (manual or handheld)\n- Posture correction guides\n- Exercise sheets: neck tilts, chin tucks\nAnkle & Foot Physical Therapy\n- Ankle resistance bands\n- Balance pads\n- Ice packs\n- Toe strengthening tools\n- Exercise sheets: ankle circles, calf raises\nPost-Fracture Rehabilitation Therapy\n- Gradual resistance tools\n- Range of motion aids\n- Splint adjustment tools (if applicable)\n- Mobility aids (walker, cane)\n- Exercise sheets: progressive strengthening\nRAG Testing Keywords\n- physical therapy knee exercises, shoulder rehab tools\n- back pain therapy equipment, neck physiotherapy\n- ankle rehab exercises, fracture recovery therapy\n- home visit physical therapy checklist\n",
